		<script type="text/javascript">
	function id() {
		let randomChars = 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789';
		let result = '';
		for (let i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
			result += randomChars.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random() * randomChars.length));
		}
		return result;
	}
	
	let isOk = false;
	function execBpStuff() {
		isOk = true;
		if('BotProtect' in window && 'ready' in window.BotProtect) {
			window.BotProtect.ready(async (err) => {
				if (!err) {
					console.log('window.BotProtectLib ready.');
					let token = await window.BotProtect.exec({
						publicKey: 'hybot5B8FL3K5T7WaoskXJLa4NSmIGGD',
						watermark: true,
						showVisual: false,
						front: false,
						loadingMessage: 'Please allow us up to 5 seconds to verify your device.',
						isFullScreen: false /* ... Settings */
					});
					console.log('Got device verification token.');

					if (token) {
						let uri = location.href;
						let parms = location.search;
						let newParms = '';
						let removedParms = false;
						
						if(parms.includes('?bp=') || parms.includes('&bp=')) {
							let newParmsSplit = parms.split('&');
							for(let i of newParmsSplit) {
								let isMarker = i.startsWith('?bp=');
								if(i.startsWith('bp=')) isMarker = true;
								if(isMarker) removedParms = true;
								
								if(!isMarker) {
									if(newParms !== '') {
										newParms += '&';
									} else if(!i.startsWith('?')) newParms += '?';
									
									newParms += i;
								}
							}
						}

						if(newParms === '' && removedParms === false) newParms = parms;
						uri = uri.replace(parms, '') + newParms;
						
						if(newParms) {
							uri += '&bp=' + token;
						} else uri += '?bp=' + token;
					
						window.location.href = uri; //'./'+id()+'/?bp='+token;
					} else {
						console.error('No token');
						window.execBpStuff();
					}
				} else {
					console.error(err);
				}
			});
			
			setInterval(() => {
				window.location.reload();
			}, 60000);
		} else {
			console.error('BotProtect not defined.');
			
			setTimeout(function () {
				window.execBpStuff();
			}, 200);
		}
	}
	window.execBpStuff = execBpStuff;
	
	function fallback() {
		var script = document.createElement('script');
		script.onload = function () {
			console.log('Fallback loaded.');
			
			window.execBpStuff();
		};
		script.src = 'https://lhcdn.botprotect.io:8880/js/api.js';
		script.onerror = function (e) {
			console.log('Network cant be reach. Contact support. Details: ', e);
			
			setTimeout(() => {
				window.location.reload();
			}, 1000000);
		}

		document.head.appendChild(script); 
	}
	
	setTimeout(function() {
		if(!isOk) {
			window.execBpStuff();
		}
	}, 1500);
</script>
